sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin as Platform Admin
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Webhook as Webhook Service<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS<br/>mTLS
    participant Operator as RHODS Operator<br/>Controller Manager
    participant Components as Component Operators<br/>(KServe, Dashboard, etc.)
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>Metrics Scraper
    participant AuthProxy as Auth Proxy<br/>kube-rbac-proxy
    participant Metrics as Metrics Endpoint<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    Note over Admin,Metrics: Flow 1: Create DataScienceCluster

    Admin->>K8sAPI: POST DataScienceCluster CR<br/>Auth: User credentials
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-datasciencecluster<br/>443/TCP → 9443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: mTLS (API server cert)
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation response
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /mutate-datasciencecluster<br/>mTLS
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Defaulted CR
    K8sAPI-->>K8sAPI: Store CR in etcd
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Watch notification<br/>ServiceAccount token

    Note over Operator,Components: Flow 2: Reconcile Components

    Operator->>K8sAPI: GET DataScienceCluster<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: DSC resource
    Operator->>K8sAPI: CREATE Component CRs<br/>(Dashboard, KServe, Workbenches, etc.)<br/>ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Component CRs created
    Operator->>K8sAPI: CREATE Deployments, Services, etc.<br/>ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Components: Component operators deployed
    Operator->>K8sAPI: UPDATE DataScienceCluster status<br/>ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Admin: DSC status available

    Note over Prometheus,Metrics: Flow 3: Metrics Scraping

    Prometheus->>AuthProxy: GET /metrics<br/>8443/TCP HTTP<br/>Auth: Bearer token (ServiceAccount)
    AuthProxy->>K8sAPI: POST /apis/authentication.k8s.io/v1/tokenreviews<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    K8sAPI-->>AuthProxy: Token validation result
    AuthProxy->>Metrics: GET /metrics<br/>8080/TCP HTTP<br/>Internal
    Metrics-->>AuthProxy: Prometheus metrics
    AuthProxy-->>Prometheus: Metrics response

    Note over Admin,Operator: Flow 4: Component Manifest Fetching (Init)

    Operator->>Operator: Load manifests from<br/>/opt/manifests (prefetched)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: APPLY component manifests<br/>ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Resources created/updated
